    -#  IMPORTANT: HTRI understands the importance of protecting personal information you supply to us via the heatbooking.com website (the “Site”). Such information may include your name and contact details; your clients’ names and contact details; and information related to the booking of hotel rooms for your clients (collectively, the “personal information”). HTRI will use the personal information to perform the purpose described in the contract executed between Innovative Transport Group, Inc. and HTRI dated March 15, 2021 (the “agreement”).  Personal information will be used in accordance with the disclosures in this Privacy Policy, as revised from time to time. Please read this Privacy Policy before accessing and using this Site or otherwise providing personal information to us.
